data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Phase 6 of Florence Gardens, crafted by the renowned Elliott Homes and built just last year. This immaculate property boasts a perfect blend of modern design and comfort, offering an array of features that will make you fall in love.

As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the open layout, creating an inviting and spacious atmosphere throughout the home.  The gorgeous wood entry table is an added bonus that remains with the home. The living area is centered around a cozy gas log fireplace, with built-in shelves for your favorite books or decorative items, creating a focal point that exudes warmth and style.  The large television conveys with the home.

The heart of this home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's delight. It features granite countertops, soft-close cabinets, and a gas range that makes cooking a joy. The owners are leaving behind 3 beautifully crafted wood barstools certain to add sophisticated seating options to your home. The absence of carpet throughout the house not only enhances the aesthetic appeal but also simplifies maintenance and ensures a clean and fresh living environment.

The primary suite is a true oasis, complete with a spa-like shower that provides a rejuvenating experience after a long day. Additional upgrades, such as a tankless water heater and blackout blinds, add convenience and energy efficiency to your daily life.

The attention to detail extends to the primary closet, where wood shelves have been meticulously installed to maximize storage and organization.  The dining room chandelier was upgraded to a gorgeous light fixture sure to enhance every meal at your table.  Blinds on the back door ensure your privacy, while the front door features frosted glass for a touch of elegance and natural light.

The outdoor space is equally impressive, with a patio that includes a ceiling fan with a light, a gas line for your barbecue, and power outlets for all your outdoor entertainment needs. The two-car garage provides ample parking and the added shelves allow for storage of tools and supplies.

Living in Florence Gardens means you'll have access to a wealth of community amenities, including a pool, parks, and a stunning 27-acre lake. Whether you prefer a leisurely stroll, a refreshing dip, or a picnic with friends and family, you'll find it all right at your doorstep.

This home offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and community living. Don't miss your chance to own this remarkable property - schedule a viewing today and make this your forever home!
